Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:02.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}無限の星すらも霞むように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:08.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}勇気　心に溢れ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:18.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}いかなる時も生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:57.04,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}盛開吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:02:02.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}靜謐的森林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:08.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}剛醒來的花兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:14.06,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}如何看待這世間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:21.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}有什麼樣的感觸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:25.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}沒有什麼比真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:33.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}更加讓人心醉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:37.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}沒有什麼比真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:44.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}更加對人殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:47.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}盡情綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}隨心飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}在此瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}拼上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:02.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}遮蔽無限星空的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:08.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}勇氣充滿心間
