Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是吧 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 姐姐你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…大家的樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被選中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種現象被稱為樹海化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時間停滯下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被選為勇者的我們被送往神樹大人所創造的結界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦派遣來的風學姐將勇者適應值較高的少女收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}創立了勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是人類的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者為了讓世界免受Vertex這一神秘生命體的襲擊而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一旦Vertex抵達神樹大人 世界就會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了阻止它 我們展現出戰鬥的意志 成為神樹大人的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界說不定會毀滅 大家也面臨著危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而我卻沒能展現出意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而 友奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看著別人受到傷害 經歷苦難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其讓別人經歷這樣的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不如由我來努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者衝拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社的活動內容是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了大家鼓起勇氣做好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是讚州國中勇者社 結城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來成為勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒跟你們說真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那怎麼不早點把勇者社真正的意義告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈和樹說不定會死的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是就算勇者適應性再高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪個小隊會被神樹大人選中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在敵人來之前是無法知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為這是涉及人類存亡的頭等大事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直瞞著我們…這麼重要的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是只有我一個人無法變身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就會成為勇者社的累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對輸給恐懼的自己感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對風學姐說了過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為正是由於適應性讓我與風學姐和樹相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是因為這適應性？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以後也會很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是多了有點困難的任務而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很高興與大家相識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保護這個世界是我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倘若我也有保護我珍愛的朋友的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:07:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要欺負友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}據風學姐所說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要打倒十二隻Vertex 我們的任務也就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且大赦還派遣了經過特別訓練的夏凜加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一開始對勇者社持否定態度的夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也漸漸地敞開心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家度過著珍愛的日常 憧憬著夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要保護好這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剩下七隻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼全部都攻過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是最糟糕的襲擊模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出陣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 去殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}將積蓄的能量釋放出來 就是勇者的王牌「盛開」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}透過不斷地盛開 勇者的力量將得到增幅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦是這樣說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}面對著剩下的七隻Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們相繼地盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「盛開」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了慶祝勇者社大勝利 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目標達成之後的果汁果然就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那場戰鬥中經歷了盛開的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體都出現了異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈是味覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐是左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹是聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是左耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然大赦的醫生說應該馬上就會痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但卻完全沒有好轉的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後 我知道了勇者系統的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直在呼喚你呀 鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是想死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她的名字叫做乃木園子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她用那悲傷的眼神緊盯著我 稱呼我為鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈經歷過「盛開」對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一下開放 一下變強的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對 經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們覺得綻放盛開的花之後會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛開之後 身體應該有什麼部位會變得不方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得大赦的人們掩蓋這一系統也算是一種同情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過 我真的好想被好好告知這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是早知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就會更珍惜和朋友玩耍的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個髮帶真適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這條髮帶是非常重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只記得這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突然叫我們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有東西想給風學姐和友奈看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東…東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者絕不會死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了確認前代勇者乃木園子所言是否屬實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我使用了各種手段尋死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz28.62\move(478,250,458,-24,0,3253)}切腹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz28.62\move(528,322,508,60,41,3253)}上吊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz26.03\move(646,376,626,110,41,3253)}跳樓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frz21.5\frx320\fry354\move(788,420,776,154,41,3253)}一氧化碳中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx320\fry354\frz29.6\move(670,552,650,288,41,3253)}淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx320\fry354\frz29.6\move(706,634,686,366,41,3253)}服毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論嘗試何種方法 精靈都成功地阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}精靈並不是為了保護勇者 而是為了將勇者永遠束縛在其使命上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說 乃木園子所言屬實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的後遺症是盛開這一力量的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是供品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 樹就再也無法發出聲音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了保護別人而獻上自己的身軀進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:13:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都怪我把樹拉進勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:06.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}出会えてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:13.25,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}木漏れ日 眩しい森の中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:18.37,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}風はいつもあったかくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:25.02,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}心ほぐれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:31.12,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}こんな日々がずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:37.81,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:46.10,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}広がる空は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:50.99,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}愛や希望で溢れて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:57.50,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この声が届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:03.89,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌い続けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:14.17,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いつも　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:28.10,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この声が届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:33.90,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌い続けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:44.60,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いつも　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:06.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}慶幸與你邂逅於
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:13.25,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}光斑炫目的林間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:18.37,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}風總是那麼溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:25.02,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}心靈也隨之解放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:31.12,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}但願這樣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:37.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}永遠地持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:46.10,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如此廣闊的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:50.99,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}充滿著愛與希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:57.50,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我會不停地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:03.89,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直至傳入你心間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:14.17,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一直一直感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:28.10,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我會不停地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:33.90,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直至傳入你心間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:44.60,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一直一直感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽我說…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是說有未來的夢想了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那快告訴姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會跟別人說的 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一天會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要幹掉大赦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦欺騙了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛開的後遺症是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼非得受這份罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼非得讓樹失聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼非得放棄夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拯救了世界的代價就是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想看到風學姐傷害別人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事情怎能饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是即便是告知我們會有後遺症
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們還是會戰鬥下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了保衛世界只能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有人有別的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:46.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(504,252,240,74,0,4289)}要是沒有與勇者社的大家相遇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:46.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(462,370,216,196,35,4289)}一定也不會擁有想歌唱的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:46.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(558,560,312,398,35,4289)}能加入勇者社真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你冷靜地聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來告訴你牆壁外側的秘密 這個世界的構成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得真相還是由你自己的眼睛來見證比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她所說的都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界在宇宙規模的結界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Vertex無限再生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們一邊奉獻著身體的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一邊重複著永無止盡的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而最終…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體就像樹木一樣無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最終就像這樣被侍奉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我得出的結論是破壞牆壁打倒神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要從勇者這一祭品中擺脫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就只有破壞神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我無法忍受大家再受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼…還要堅持…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道為什麼 突然想這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不論是家裡的事還是勇者社的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把麻煩事都交給姐姐來做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 其實我想讓自己能與姐姐並肩前行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何止是並肩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知不覺間已經走到我前面了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼無法變身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不配當…朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不再作為大赦的勇者而戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從現在開始作為勇者社的一員而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會讓我們的勇者社遭到毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想看到友奈哭泣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}諸行無常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來吧 好戲從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:18:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遠處的傢伙們聽好了 近處的傢伙們看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是讚州國中二年級生 勇者社社員三好夏凜的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 吃招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這即將來臨的新世界中 風學姐和樹就不需要再戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社五準則 其五
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有志者事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜也不要再失去什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:19:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個世界 大赦的做法 有多麼淒慘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要拯救我們 就只有這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「謝謝你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我長期以來一直接受勇者的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有戰鬥才是我的存在價值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是多虧了大家 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈你能夠改變東鄉的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定能夠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我曾經作為勇者戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後失去了這段記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然我保護不了我最好的朋友 那我就做不成勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要能將一切終結 我們的人間地獄也會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其犧牲友奈和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其再次忘記這珍愛的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我永遠陪伴著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣的話就不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做了這麼過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是東鄉同學的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們去阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}絕對不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 在這關鍵的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:53.42,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要小看勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 勇者社…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\alpha&HA0&}友奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擊中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社的大家 明明也都很艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但卻為了朋友 拼盡全力 阻止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈全力衝向了我 全力抱緊了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後我們擊敗了敵人 身體功能也恢復了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.47,0:23:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我重要的回憶 也恢復了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然還不清楚為什麼會恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但至少這不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為失去的生命 並沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起去上學 學習 玩耍 回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}日常竟然是如此珍貴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很清楚 一切並沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Vertex還殘存著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道未來還會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.58,0:23:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是現在 我緊緊地擁抱著這無可替代的溫暖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}さあ　歩き出そう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.19,0:22:48.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}みんなで見た　あの空模様
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.29,0:22:51.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}光のカーテン　しめきっても
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.79,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここは暗くない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.79,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もう　分かってたの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつか終わる　この瞬間
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.88,0:23:02.69,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}とても大切で　大切で
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}目を背けていた
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.10,0:23:07.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}儚い時は
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.19,0:23:10.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっという間に過ぎて行くよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.08,0:23:12.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}これは本当に
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.12,0:23:15.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}起こった出来事？
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そのカケラを夕陽に
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.87,0:23:20.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}かざして確かめてみるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れられない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.87,0:23:25.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れちゃいけない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.63,0:23:32.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとつひとつが素晴らしい思い出
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつでも　目に浮かぶその笑顔
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.19,0:23:43.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとつひとつが奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.59,0:23:49.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここにこうして舞い降りてきたの
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.93,0:23:55.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So bright
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}來　邁開腳步吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.19,0:22:48.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}大家看到的天空
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.29,0:22:51.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}即便拉上光之簾
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.79,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這裡也並不黑暗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.79,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我現在已經明白
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這瞬間終將結束
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.88,0:23:02.69,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這是那麼的寶貴
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我不禁避開視線
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.10,0:23:07.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}夢幻般的時刻
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.19,0:23:10.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}真是轉瞬即逝
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.08,0:23:12.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這是真真正正
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.12,0:23:15.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}發生過的事嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}殘片對著夕陽
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.87,0:23:20.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}來試著確認吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這些無法忘卻
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.87,0:23:25.63,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這些不能忘卻
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.63,0:23:32.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}每每都是美妙回憶
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}總是回想起那笑容
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.19,0:23:43.59,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}每每都是一份奇蹟
Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.59,0:23:49.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就像這樣降臨於此
